Loading Data

We begin by loading the massSight package alongside two dataframes containing data from LC-MS experiments.

library(massSight)
#> 
#> Attaching package: 'massSight'
#> The following object is masked from 'package:stats':
#> 
#>     smooth
data("hp1")
data("hp2")
head(hp1) |> kableExtra::kbl()

Creating massSight objects 

hp1_ms <- create_ms_obj(hp1,
  name = "hp1",
  annot = TRUE,
  id_name = "Compound_ID",
  rt_name = "RT",
  mz_name = "MZ",
  int_name = "Intensity",
  metab_name = "Metabolite",
  has_metadata = FALSE
)
hp2_ms <- create_ms_obj(hp2,
  name = "hp2",
  annot = TRUE,
  id_name = "Compound_ID",
  rt_name = "RT",
  mz_name = "MZ",
  int_name = "Intensity",
  metab_name = "Metabolite",
  has_metadata = FALSE
)
